output directory after container completion:\n- Identifies log files by naming convention:\n  - `full.log` → type: \"full\"\n  - `llm-<step>.log` → type: \"llm\", step: \\<step\\>\n  - `<step>.log` → type: \"script\", step: \\<step\\>\n  - `container.log` → internal, not indexed\n- Creates `LogFileEntry` records in the log store\n\n### 13. Log Extraction from Containers\n\n**File: `/workspace/internal/adapters/grpc/server.go` (lines 293-307)**\n\nAfter container completion:\n1. Output files are extracted from container: `/workspace/.cloche/output/.*` → `.cloche/<run-id>/output/`\n2. Container stdout/stderr is captured: `Logs()` → `.cloche/<run-id>/output/container.log`\n3. Log files are indexed into the log store\n\n### Summary of File Paths\n\n**Core System Files:**\n- `/workspace/api/proto/cloche/v1/cloche.proto` — gRPC service definition\n- `/workspace/cmd/cloche/main.go` — CLI logs command (lines 347-432)\n- `/workspace/cmd/cloched/main.go` — Daemon initialization\n- `/workspace/internal/domain/run.go` — Run and StepExecution types\n- `/workspace/internal/ports/store.go` — RunStore, CaptureStore, LogStore interfaces\n\n**Adapter Implementations:**\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/sqlite/store.go` — SQLite implementation (runs, captures, logs tables)\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/grpc/server.go` — gRPC server with StreamLogs handler (lines 487-726)\n\n**Log Capture:**\n- `/workspace/internal/agent/runner.go` — In-container agent logging\n- `/workspace/internal/host/executor.go` — Host workflow step execution and logging\n- `/workspace/internal/logstream/logstream.go` — Unified log writer\n- `/workspace/internal/logstream/broadcaster.go` — Live log pub/sub broadcaster\n- `/workspace/internal/protocol/status.go` — Status message protocol\n\n**Adapters:**\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go` — Prompt agent with streaming\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/generic/generic.go` — Generic script adapter with streaming\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/docker/runtime.go` — Container runtime (output extraction)\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go` — HTTP API for logs and tasks\n\nThis architecture enables:\n1. **Real-time log streaming** via the broadcaster for active runs\n2. **Persistent log storage** in the database and filesystem\n3. **Flexible log filtering** by step and log type\n4. **Multi-source output** from agent, script, and status messages\n5. **Seamless switching** between live streaming and historical log replay"}],"totalDurationMs":49727,"totalTokens":83012,"totalToolUseCount":32,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2361,"cache_read_input_tokens":77839,"output_tokens":2808,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2361},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
